statements: SELECT * FROM CuisineReport;
SELECT cuisine_name, profit FROM CuisineReport ORDER BY profit DESC;
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales, total_expenses, profit FROM CuisineReport WHERE total_sales > 5000;
SELECT cuisine_name, profit FROM CuisineReport WHERE profit >= 500 ORDER BY profit ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales, total_expenses, profit FROM CuisineReport WHERE cuisine_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales FROM CuisineReport WHERE total_sales > 1000 ORDER BY total_sales DESC;
SELECT * FROM CuisineReport WHERE total_sales >= 5000 AND total_expenses <= 3000 ORDER BY profit DESC;
SELECT cuisine_name, SUM(total_sales) AS total_sales_sum FROM CuisineReport GROUP BY cuisine_name;
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales, total_expenses, profit FROM CuisineReport WHERE profit > 5000 ORDER BY total_sales ASC;
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales, profit FROM CuisineReport WHERE total_expenses < 2000 ORDER BY total_sales DESC, profit ASC;
SELECT * FROM Cuisines ORDER BY cuisine_name ASC;
SELECT cuisine_name, country FROM Cuisines WHERE sales_data > 10000;
SELECT * FROM Cuisines WHERE expenses < 5000;
SELECT cuisine_name, sales_data FROM Cuisines WHERE country = 'Italy';
SELECT cuisine_name, country, sales_data, expenses FROM Cuisines WHERE sales_data > expenses;
SELECT * FROM Cuisines WHERE country = 'Italy';
SELECT cuisine_name, sales_data FROM Cuisines ORDER BY sales_data DESC;
SELECT cuisine_name, country, sales_data, expenses FROM Cuisines WHERE sales_data > 5000 AND country = 'France' ORDER BY expenses ASC;
SELECT * FROM Reports WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-28' AND profitability > 0.1 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT c.cuisine_name, r.date, r.profitability FROM Reports r JOIN Cuisines c ON r.cuisine_id = c.cuisine_id WHERE r.profitability > 0.2 ORDER BY r.profitability DESC, c.cuisine_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM CuisineSales ORDER BY total_sales DESC;
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales FROM CuisineSales WHERE year = 2021;
SELECT cuisine_name, net_profit FROM CuisineProfitability WHERE year = 2020 ORDER BY net_profit ASC;
SELECT cuisine_name, ingredient_cost, labor_cost, rent_cost FROM CuisineExpenses WHERE year = 2019;
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales, net_profit FROM CuisineSales s JOIN CuisineProfitability p ON s.cuisine_id = p.cuisine_id;
SELECT cuisine_id, cuisine_name, total_sales, year FROM CuisineSales WHERE total_sales > 10000 ORDER BY total_sales DESC;
SELECT cuisine_id, cuisine_name, ingredient_cost, labor_cost, rent_cost, year FROM CuisineExpenses WHERE year = 2021;
SELECT cuisine_id, cuisine_name, net_profit, year FROM CuisineProfitability WHERE net_profit < 5000 ORDER BY net_profit ASC;
SELECT cuisine_id, cuisine_name, total_sales, year FROM CuisineSales WHERE year = 2020 AND total_sales BETWEEN 5000 AND 10000;
SELECT cuisine_id, cuisine_name, total_sales, year FROM CuisineSales WHERE year = 2019 OR year = 2020 ORDER BY year ASC, total_sales DESC;
SELECT * FROM Sales ORDER BY sale_id DESC;
SELECT cuisine_type, sale_amount FROM Sales WHERE cuisine_type = 'Italian';
SELECT sale_id, sale_amount, cuisine_type FROM Sales WHERE sale_amount > 1000;
SELECT * FROM CuisineProfitability WHERE net_profit < 0 ORDER BY total_sales DESC;
SELECT report_name, report_date FROM Reports WHERE cuisine_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM Sales ORDER BY sale_amount DESC, cuisine_type
SELECT cuisine_type, SUM(sale_amount) AS total_sales FROM Sales GROUP BY cuisine_type HAVING total_sales > 5000
SELECT cp.cuisine_type, cp.total_sales, e.expense_category, e.expense_amount FROM CuisineProfitability cp JOIN Expenses e ON cp.cuisine_id = e.expense_id WHERE cp.total_sales > cp.total_expenses

SELECT r.report_name, r.report_date, cp.cuisine_type, cp.net_profit FROM Reports r JOIN CuisineProfitability cp ON r.cuisine_id = cp.cuisine_id WHERE YEAR(r.report_date) = 2021 ORDER BY cp.net_profit DESC
SELECT * FROM CuisineProfitability ORDER BY total_sales ASC
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales FROM cuisine_sales;
SELECT * FROM cuisine_expenses WHERE expense_type = 'Marketing';
SELECT cuisine_id, total_sales, sales_date FROM cuisine_sales ORDER BY sales_date DESC;
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales, sales_date FROM cuisine_sales WHERE total_sales > 1000;
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales, sales_date FROM cuisine_sales WHERE sales_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';
SELECT cuisine_name, total_sales FROM cuisine_sales
SELECT * FROM cuisine_expenses WHERE expense_amount > 1000 ORDER BY expense_date DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT cp.cuisine_id, cp.net_profit, cl.location_name FROM cuisine_profit cp JOIN cuisine_locations cl ON cp.cuisine_id = cl.cuisine_id

SELECT cc.category_name, cs.total_sales, cp.net_profit FROM cuisine_categories cc LEFT JOIN cuisine_sales cs ON cc.category_id = cs.cuisine_id LEFT JOIN cuisine_profit cp ON cc.category_id = cp.cuisine_id
SELECT cl.country, SUM(ce.expense_amount) AS total_expenses FROM cuisine_expenses ce JOIN cuisine_locations cl ON ce.cuisine_id = cl.cuisine_id GROUP BY cl.country ORDER BY total_expenses DESC
